# Cursor Rules - Indonesian Documentation

## Language & Tone
- Formal Bahasa Indonesia (EYD)
- Professional, descriptive, informative
- Mix: English tech terms + Indonesian explanation
- Example: "WebSocket connection", "message queue management"

## Key Connectors
- "yaitu:" = definition/elaboration
- "antara lain:" = list/examples
- "dengan demikian," = conclusion
- "yang mencakup" = component details
- "dimana" = condition/state
- "serta" = additional info
- "untuk" = purpose

## Code Comments

### Function/Method
```javascript
/**
 * [Function purpose & behavior] dengan [implementation detail]
 * @param {Type} name - Explanation
 * @returns {Type} Return detail
 */
```

### Inline
```javascript
// Validasi input dengan checking type dan format
// untuk memastikan data sesuai requirement
```

### Complex Logic
```javascript
/**
 * Mapping priority ke weight value untuk queue processing
 * dimana critical = 1, high = 2, medium = 3, low = 4
 */
```

